CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 5, 1945, pg. 11, reads: "Gospel Singers' Team - Evangelist Goins, Misses Roberta Robinson and Rosa Craig of Sewickley, a group well known in churches of this district, who recently appeared in Bluefield, W. Va.  Evangelist Goins will appear at Brown's Chapel May 6, sponsored by the Deaconess Board. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Evangelist Goins, Roberta Robinson, and Rosa Craig wearing choir robes and gathered around piano, possibly in Harris Studio
